These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
Nationality: argentine, french, italian, british
1. Nationality:french is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:british is between Nationality:argentine and Nationality:french##2
3. Nationality:british is on the right of Nationality:argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | argentine | british | french | italian |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
Food: asparagus, cabbage, plum, cucumber
1. Food:asparagus is on the left of Food:cucumber##1
2. Food:cabbage is in an odd position##4
3. Food:cabbage is on the left or right of Food:asparagus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | cabbage | asparagus | cucumber | plum |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
Movie-Genre: thriller, family, action, disaster
1. Movie-Genre:disaster is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:thriller##3
2. Movie-Genre:thriller is in an odd position##4
3. Movie-Genre:action is between Movie-Genre:disaster and Movie-Genre:family##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | disaster | action | family |

 #################################
 
