.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-19::.
Food: cucumber, onion, asparagus, watermelon
1. Food:onion == Food:onion##1
2. Food:watermelon is on the left or right of Food:asparagus##3
3. Food:asparagus is on the far left or far right##3
4. Food:cucumber is in an even position##4
5. Food:watermelon is on the left of Food:onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | asparagus | watermelon | onion | cucumber |

